data.description: Welcome to this charming one story home situated on a quiet cul-de-sac street. Features include a stone & brick facade, open-concept living, high ceilings, luxury vinyl plank flooring, 3 bedrooms & 2 full baths. The kitchen boasts a walk-in pantry, large island with seating space, stainless steel appliances & granite countertops. The primary suite offers a dual-sink vanity, soaking tub, separate shower & generous walk-in closet. 2" blinds throughout, smart lights, neutral colors, extra long driveway for ample parking, whole home gutters, automatic sprinkler system & more. This home is within walking distance to the community pool & playground. Ideally located with easy access to 99, 59 & 45. Don't miss this one!
